item.title: Trump says he and Putin will meet in Hungary to discuss war in Ukraine
item.description: President Donald Trump this week said that he is considering sending Tomahawk missiles to Ukraine to ratchet up pressure on Russia to end the war.

item.description: Trump recently imposed a $100,00 fee on temporary visas for highly skilled workers in a push to have American companies hire more domestic workers.

item.title: John Bolton indicted by grand jury, latest Trump foe to face criminal charges
